sequenceDiagram
    participant S as Student
    participant F as Backend (Flask)
    participant MS as Microsoft Azure AD
    participant DB as PostgreSQL

    S->>F: GET /auth/login
    F->>F: Generuj state (uuid)
    F-->>S: Redirect na URL logowania MS

    S->>MS: Logowanie (email + haslo uczelni)
    MS-->>S: Redirect /auth/callback?code=...&state=...

    S->>F: GET /auth/callback?code=...
    F->>F: Weryfikacja state

    alt state nieprawidlowy
        F-->>S: Blad - sprobuj ponownie
    else state poprawny
        F->>MS: acquire_token_by_authorization_code
        MS-->>F: access_token + id_token (claims)

        F->>MS: GET /v1.0/me (Graph API)
        MS-->>F: displayName, email, oid

        F->>DB: Szukaj usera po ms_oid
        alt user nie istnieje
            F->>DB: Utworz nowego usera (rola: student)
        else user istnieje
            F->>DB: Aktualizuj email, imie, last_login_at
        end

        DB-->>F: User object
        F->>F: Zapisz sesje (id, email, rola)
        F-->>S: Redirect /dashboard
    end
